{"tid":2134714,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華爾街日報：微軟欲收購TikTok","createTime":"2020-08-01T02:34:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T02:47:54.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"293df7203de2256c41a474f279b450eaba1b44a3","tid":2134714,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:34:27.000Z","msg":"報道指微軟欲收購TikTok<br />\n<br />\n美國正研究禁用中國社交應用程式抖音的海外版TikTok之際，微軟正與TikTok母公司字節跳動洽談收購行動。華爾街日報引述消息指，收購金額涉及數十億美元，美國當局正在進行安全審查。另有報道指，交易最快可能在周一完成。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普指，正研究多個選項，包括可能禁用TikTok。他離開白宮前往佛羅里達州時表示，正發生很多事情，將會拭目以待。報道引述消息人士說，特朗普要求字節跳動拆售TikTok。由於TikTok在美國越來越受歡迎，華府官員關注中國政府可能透過這個應用程式，取得美國民眾的個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2350063\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2350063&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOTe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=755bac3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2350063</a>"},{"pid":"3c829ee39ee5acddfc6ab1527440a05229d10004","tid":2134714,"uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:35:41.000Z","msg":"微軟又係奶共奶到"},{"pid":"1e5fc66aa84292868ff20620d68a0090a2c25095","tid":2134714,"uid":87573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:37:32.000Z","msg":"MS死亡之吻"},{"pid":"40b3afc72490c17253f32859fc237307de280a2d","tid":2134714,"uid":289708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:38:32.000Z","msg":"買到都唔識點run<br />\nM$搞social networking真係唔耍家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a464dbc91c8f8bd6f6c0a766e2a0569a45f73d2e","tid":2134714,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:38:34.000Z","msg":"奶都唔夠，仲要俾錢佢使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710f35407d7051ca10b7e0b4a035e4c99ffe51d0","tid":2134714,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply